&lt;p&gt;then added the classes to the parent which were required.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre class=&quot;default s-code-block&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs language-xml&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-name&quot;&gt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-attr&quot;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt;=&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot;&gt;&quot;row fsi-row-lg-level fsi-row-md-level&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
